# E1 Recovery Manifest

**Unit:** E1 — Recover terminal UI worktree  
**Branch:** `recover/E1-terminal-ui-worktree`  
**Epic:** epic_E — BytePort: terminal UI, tools CLI, otel, governance  
**Recovered:** 2026-06-25  

## Source

The terminal UI work originated from stash side-219 on a now-retired branch
(`chore/l4-64-byteport-hex-2026-06-11`). It was partially recovered to
`chore/A11-recover-byteport-stash-0-terminal-ui` and merged into `origin/main`
via commit `68c4ec2c`.

## Recovered Files

| File | Lines | Description |
|------|-------|-------------|
| `crates/byteport-transport/src/ports/ui.rs` | 389 | Generic `UiPort` trait with `UiView`, `PromptMessage`, `PromptResponse`, `UiError`, and `MockUiAdapter` for testing |
| `crates/byteport-transport/src/ports/terminal_ui.rs` | 370 | `TerminalUiAdapter` — TTY/REPL adapter implementing `UiPort` with interactive and non-interactive modes |
| `crates/byteport-transport/src/ports/mod.rs` | 5 | Module wiring (`pub mod ui; pub mod terminal_ui;`) |

